data.description: Get ready to be blown away by this gem of a property that's just waiting for you to call it "home sweet home". Let me walk you through the features that'll make you fall head over heels for this place. 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms: Perfectly designed for both relaxation and functionality, providing ample space for your family to thrive. Family Room: A spacious, inviting retreat to unwind and entertain, adorned with an electric fireplace, setting the stage for cozy evenings with loved ones. Your Own Backyard Oasis: Step outside and into your private paradise, where a large fenced-in backyard, huge deck, and patio are just begging for BBQs and summer gatherings. Bonus points for the gazebo, perfect for those lazy Sunday afternoons, additional outdoor amenities such as a trampoline and firepit, promising endless enjoyment and memories to be made under the open sky. Updates Galore: Impeccably updated bath fixtures, toilet, and shower door add a touch of luxury, while recent upgrades including HVAC (2019) and Roof & Siding (2018) ensure worry-free living for years to come. 2.5 Car Garage: Ample space for vehicles and storage, ensuring both convenience and peace of mind. This dreamy home won't be on the market for long. Schedule your showing today and get ready to start living the good life. Home is in great shape, but selling AS-IS. No Fha, Conventional financing or cash offers only.
